		"description": "<p>You combine the scholarship of a wizard with the commitment of a herald. This is a difficult path tread by few, but you have embarked on it. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Strength, Intelligence or Charisma score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>When you use @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.iqlgotutphoratct]{Arcane Recovery}, you also regain a number of @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.my42mip0qc35rcp2]{Lay on Hands} points equal to your herald level.</li>\n<li>You can cast a herald spell as a ritual if that spell has the ritual tag and you have the spell prepared.</li>\n<li>You gain proficiency with the Arcana and Religion skills. If you are already proficient, you gain an expertise die instead. You also gain a skill specialty of your choice with each skill.</li>\n</ul>",
